sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Copilot
    participant LS as list_symbols
    participant A as analyze
    participant H as highlight
    participant E as export

    U->>C: codewalker-all プロンプト選択
    C->>LS: list_symbols(path, level)
    LS-->>C: targets + targets.json 保存

    U->>U: targets.json 編集（任意）
    C->>LS: list_symbols(fromFile=true)
    LS-->>C: pending targets

    loop 各ターゲット
        C->>A: analyze(filePath, symbolName)
        A-->>C: sourceCode + blocks
        C->>H: highlight(blocks, annotations, explanations)
        H-->>C: OK
        C->>E: export(batchMode=true)
        E-->>C: saved
    end

    Note over C: 完了サマリー報告
